  <div class="pillars">
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">01</div>
      <h3>Community &amp; Connection</h3>
      <p>We create intentional spaces for Black Denisonians to find each other — across generations, across geographies, across difference.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">02</div>
      <h3>Legacy &amp; Scholarship</h3>
      <p>We invest in the next generation through scholarships, mentorship, and a permanent giving infrastructure that doesn't depend on any one institution.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillar">
      <div class="pillar-num">03</div>
      <h3>Power &amp; Advocacy</h3>
      <p>We organize. We speak. We hold Denison accountable to its commitments to Black students, faculty, and the broader community.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
