<!-- VISION -->
<section class="vision-section">
  <div class="vision-left">
    <div class="vision-eyebrow">Our Vision</div>
    <blockquote class="vision-quote">"A Denison where Black students don't just survive — they lead."</blockquote>
  </div>
  <div class="vision-body">
    <p>The Black Alumni Association of Denison was built by generations of graduates who refused to let their connection to the institution — or to each other — fade after graduation.</p>
    <p>We are now building infrastructure: a scholarship DAF, an organized giving circle, a newsletter, and systems that outlast any single leader or class year.</p>
